  "body": "<p>Truly one of the best parts of what I do for work (how lucky am I to have this job?!) is meeting creative and kind people. I am always humbled by their enthusiasm and kind words. Some of them even ask me to sign stuff! (Blushing). So when the opportunity presents itself - an owner reaching out and inviting me to their store to teach classes - my heart skips a beat. Tammy, the spunky owner of <a href=\"http://www.paperniche.com/\">Paper Niche</a> reached out a couple months ago and amidst all the craziness, we planned a class for Friday night and 2 classes on Saturday. There were even a few people who signed up for all 3 classes. We played with <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_mister%2520huey%2527s_/\">Studio Calico Mister Hueys</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/126957-cascade-amy-tangerine-sketchbook-scene-glitter-foam-thickers-stickers/%3Ffilters%3D_thickers_\">Thickers</a>, watercolors, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_mistable_/stickers/\">Mistables</a> and all kinds of fun stuff. How lucky I was to spend the bulk of my weekend surrounded by crafty hands and smiling faces.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6a-IMG_0094-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5eb58cacbdcbb427.jpg?v=1782530504\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"6b-IMG_0099-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cf5d8cb698c2c022.jpg?v=1782530507\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6c-IMG_0102-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d5682f0b03c7d78a.jpg?v=1782530510\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6d-Untitled-1-600x399.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/57680a5f8512a874.jpg?v=1782530512\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6e-IMG_0108-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7364f9bde40cc0ac.jpg?v=1782530515\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6f-IMG_0113-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e912687d03ea9baa.jpg?v=1782530518\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6g-IMG_0120-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9032b1437a25f58e.jpg?v=1782530521\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6h-IMG_0117-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/898dc725b4ff80e6.jpg?v=1782530524\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6i-IMG_0134-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7dc1ea9a66897b20.jpg?v=1782530526\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6j-IMG_0136-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a4323a37cfc5ca53.jpg?v=1782530529\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6k-IMG_0139-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/267a9cd11b91ae4a.jpg?v=1782530532\"/>"
